If <code>term1</code> and <code>term2</code> are both 
                <a data-cite="RDF12-CONCEPTS#dfn-triple-term" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf12-concepts/#dfn-triple-term" id="ref-for-index-term-triple-term-9">triple terms</a>,
                apply the function <code>sameValue</code> pair-wise to each of the components.
                Return TRUE if each component pair returns TRUE;
                produce a type error if any component pair produces an error;
                otherwise return FALSE.
